columns.text:
In the first question, the DOL and the operating cashflow are given. Since we need to solve for the fixed cost, we can use this formula for DOL:

$$\begin{aligned}
\text{DOL}&=1+\dfrac{\text{FC}}{\text{OCF}}
\end{aligned}$$

For the next set of questions, we have changes in the valeus of our quantity. Therefore, we will use the other formula for DOL:

$$\begin{aligned}
\text{DOL}&=\dfrac{\Delta \text{OCF}}{\Delta \text{Q}}
\end{aligned}$$
